  Title: Toxic Fog
  Description: Thick mist rolls through the corridors. Breathing it in hurts your
    throats and visibility reduces to an arms length.
  Targeting: 2
  BaseTimeCost: 0.15
  Choices:
  - Label: Press on cautiously
    VagueHint: Some progress is better than none. But breathing in the fog could
      be dangerous.
